MAPPLET.DESCRIPTION: Mapplet to get the SAP ITEM_ID
MAPPLET.NAME: ML_SAP_ITEM

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on ITEM table to get ITEM_ID
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM.ITEM_ID) AS ITEM_ID, TRIM(ITEM.SAP_GRID_VALUE) AS SAP_GRID_VALUE, TRIM(ITEM.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM) as SAP_MATERIAL_NUM FROM ITEM WHERE DIVISION_GROUP='slsp' AND ITEM_TYPE_CODE = 'SEL' AND TRIM(ITEM.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM) IS NOT NULL GROUP BY TRIM(ITEM.SAP_GRID_VALUE), TRIM(ITEM.SAP_MATERIAL_NUM)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on SAP_ITEM based on the input Style, color, Size, Attribut_cd and get the Material_num and Grid_value. Material_status_code, output either one row.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SAP_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(MATERIAL_NUM) AS MATERIAL_NUM, GRID_VALUE AS GRID_VALUE, LEGACY_STYLE AS LEGACY_STYLE,LEGACY_COLOR AS LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE AS LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE AS LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE FROM (SELECT MATERIAL_NUM, GRID_VALUE, LEGACY_STYLE, LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE, RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY LEGACY_STYLE, LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE ORDER BY CASE WHEN MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE = '50' THEN 1 WHEN MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE > '50' AND MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE < '99' THEN 2 WHEN MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE > '0' AND MATERIAL_STATUS_CODE < '50' THEN 3 ELSE 4 END , CASE WHEN LEGACY_PUTUP_CODE = '000' THEN 1 ELSE 2 END , MATERIAL_NUM ) RNK FROM SAP_ITEM ) WHERE RNK=1 GROUP BY GRID_VALUE, LEGACY_STYLE, LEGACY_COLOR, LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE, LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: LEGACY_STYLE = I_STYLE AND LEGACY_COLOR = I_COLOR AND LEGACY_ATTRIBUTE = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD AND LEGACY_SIZE_CODE_SCALE = I_SIZE_CD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, TRIM(STYLE_NUM) as STYLE_NUM, TRIM(COLOR_CODE) as COLOR_CODE, TRIM(ATTRIBUTION_CODE) as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, TRIM(SIZE_CODE) AS SIZE_CODE FROM ITEM WHERE DIVISION_GROUP = 'slsp' and item_type_code = 'SEL' GROUP BY TRIM(STYLE_NUM),TRIM(COLOR_CODE),TRIM(ATTRIBUTION_CODE),TRIM(SIZE_CODE)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_NUM = I_STYLE AND COLOR_CODE = I_COLOR AND SIZE_CODE = I_SIZE_CODE AND ATTRIBUTION_CODE = I_ATTRIBUTE_COD

TRANSFORMATION.NAME: ML_SAP_ITEM

MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This mapping is used to load the 'TurnKey' data from the 'STG_TSR_SOURCED_ORDERS' table into the target tables 'BIWIP_INVENTORY' and 'WIP_EXPLODED' for MFB records.
MAPPING.NAME: m_BIWIP_INV_TRNKEY_MFB

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CD = BOM_PARENT_STYLE AND COLOR_CD = BOM_PARENT_COLOR AND SIZE_CD = BOM_PARENT_SIZE AND ATTRIBUTE_CD = BOM_PARENT_ATTRIBUTE

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This Source Quailfier is used to pull the records from source.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_TSR_SOURCED_ORDERS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRIM(STSO.STYLE_CD) AS STYLE_CD , TRIM(STSO.COLOR_CD) AS COLOR_CD , TRIM(STSO.SIZE_CD) AS SIZE_CD , TRIM(ATTRIBUTE_CD) as ATTRIBUTE_CD, STSO.AS_OF_DATE AS AS_OF_DATE, SUM(STSO.OPEN_QTY) AS UNITS_QTY ,DESTINATION_CD ,ORDER_ID ,LINEITEM_ID ,DC_DUE_DATE, TRIM(STSO.PLANT_CD) FROM STAGING.STG_TSR_SOURCED_ORDERS STSO WHERE STSO.AS_OF_DATE = (SELECT AS_OF_DATE FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE DAY_DATE = TRUNC(SYSDATE)-1 ) AND STSO.OPEN_QTY > 0 AND STSO.DIVISION_CD IN ('PTY','BRA') GROUP BY TRIM(STSO.STYLE_CD), TRIM(STSO.COLOR_CD), TRIM(STSO.SIZE_CD),TRIM(ATTRIBUTE_CD), STSO.AS_OF_DATE, DESTINATION_CD, ORDER_ID, LINEITEM_ID, DC_DUE_DATE, TRIM(STSO.PLANT_CD)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: this source qualifier is used to pull all the necessary columns from STYLE table.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STYLE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: Select trim(style_cd) AS STYLE_CD from style where origin_type_cd = 'S'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This lookup is used to fetch facility_id from slba_facility
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_FACILITY1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT NVL(SLSP_FACILITY_TYPE_ID,FACILITY_TYPE_ID) AS FACILITY_TYPE_ID, FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE FROM
(SELECT SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_TYPE_ID AS FACILITY_TYPE_ID, Null as SLSP_FACILITY_TYPE_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE FROM SLBA_FACILITY
UNION ALL
SELECT NULL AS FACILITY_TYPE_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_TYPE_ID as SLSP_FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE FROM SLBA_FACILITY WHERE DIVISION_GROUP='slsp')

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: this joiner is used on the tables STG_PSCT_OW_BOM and STYLE
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: JNR_STG_OW_BOM_STYLE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, TRIM(ITEM.COLOR_CODE) as COLOR_CODE, TRIM(ITEM.SIZE_CODE) as SIZE_CODE, TRIM(ITEM.STYLE_NUM) as STYLE_NUM, TRIM(NVL(ITEM.CUP_SIZE,'')) as CUP_SIZE FROM ITEM WHERE DIVISION_GROUP='mfb'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: COLOR_CODE = I_EXTERNAL_COLOR AND SIZE_CODE = I_EXTERNAL_SIZE AND STYLE_NUM = I_EXTERNAL_STYLE AND CUP_SIZE = I_EXTERNAL_VERSION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, NVL(SUBSTR(ITEM.SKU,1,14),' ') as SKU FROM ITEM WHERE TRIM(SUBSTR(ITEM.SKU,15,2)) <> '00' AND ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP='sli' GROUP BY NVL(SUBSTR(ITEM.SKU,1,14),' ')

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: this expression transformations is used to get all the columns from the source and lookup together.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_ADDITIONAL_DATA

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This performs lookup on EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF table.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_STYLE) as EXTERNAL_STYLE, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_COLOR) as EXTERNAL_COLOR, TRIM(SUBSTR(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_SIZE,1,3)) as EXTERNAL_SIZE, CASE WHEN TRIM(EXTERNAL_VERSION)='NOCUP' THEN '' ELSE TRIM(EXTERNAL_VERSION) END as EXTERNAL_VERSION, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_SKU) as EXTERNAL_SKU, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.STYLE_CD) as STYLE_CD, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.COLOR_CD) as COLOR_CD, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.SIZE_CD) as SIZE_CD , TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.ATTRIBUTE_CD) as ATTRIBUTE_CD FROM EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CD = I_STYLE_CD AND COLOR_CD = I_COLOR_CD AND SIZE_CD = I_SIZE_CD AND ATTRIBUTE_CD = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: this source qualifier is used to pull all the necessary columns from STG_PSCT_OW_BOM table.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_PSCT_OW_BOM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT trim(PARENT_STYLE) as PARENT_STYLE, trim(PARENT_COLOR) as PARENT_COLOR, trim(PARENT_ATTRIBUTE) as PARENT_ATTRIBUTE, trim(PARENT_SIZE) as PARENT_SIZE, trim(COMP_STYLE_CD) as COMP_STYLE_CD, trim(COMP_COLOR_CD) as COMP_COLOR_CD, trim(COMP_ATTRIBUTE_CD) as COMP_ATTRIBUTE_CD, trim(COMP_SIZE_CD) as COMP_SIZE_CD, round ( usage / (sum(usage) over( partition by TRIM(parent_style), TRIM(parent_color), TRIM(parent_size), TRIM(parent_attribute))) , 4) as comp_factor FROM STG_PSCT_OW_BOM where trim(parent_style) || trim(parent_color) || trim(parent_attribute) || trim(parent_size) <> trim(comp_style_cd) || trim(comp_color_cd) || trim(comp_attribute_cd) || trim(comp_size_cd)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on LKP_WIP_INV_STATUS to get required fields
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_WIP_INV_STATUS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
select min(w.INVENTORY_GRP_CD) as INVENTORY_GRP_CD , we.INVENTORY_STAT as IN_INVENTORY_STAT
FROM WIP_INV_GRP w,wip_inv_status we
where w.INVENTORY_GRP_CD = we.INVENTORY_GRP_CD and we.INVENTORY_STAT = 'OS' group by we.INVENTORY_STAT

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This performs lookup on EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF table for Intimates data.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF_IN

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT NVL(SUBSTR(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.EXTERNAL_SKU,1,14),' ') as EXTERNAL_SKU, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.STYLE_CD) as STYLE_CD, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.COLOR_CD) as COLOR_CD, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.SIZE_CD) as SIZE_CD, TRIM(EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF.ATTRIBUTE_CD) as ATTRIBUTE_CD FROM EXTERNAL_SKU_XREF

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: STYLE_CD = I_STYLE_CD AND COLOR_CD = I_COLOR_CD AND SIZE_CD = I_SIZE_CD AND ATTRIBUTE_CD = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on LKP_FACILITY_TYPE to get required fields
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_FACILITY_TYPE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select d.description as DESCRIPTION, f.facility_code as FACILITY_CODE, from facility_type d,facility f where d.facility_type_id= f.facility_type_id

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This lookup is used to fetch facility_id from slba_facility
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_FACILITY

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT NVL(SLSP_FACILITY_ID,FACILITY_ID) as FACILITY_ID, FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE FROM
(SELECT SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID as FACILITY_ID, Null as SLSP_FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE FROM SLBA_FACILITY
UNION ALL
SELECT NULL as FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_ID as SLSP_FACILITY_ID, SLBA_FACILITY.FACILITY_CODE as FACILITY_CODE FROM SLBA_FACILITY WHERE DIVISION_GROUP='slsp')

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup on LKP_WIP_INV_GRP to get required fields
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_WIP_INV_GRP

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT
w.INVENTORY_GRP_DESC as INVENTORY_GRP_DESC,
min(w.inventory_grp_cd) as IN_INVENTORY_GRP_CD , we.INVENTORY_STAT as INVENTORY_STAT
FROM WIP_INV_GRP w,wip_inv_status we
where w.INVENTORY_GRP_CD = we.inventory_grp_cd and we.INVENTORY_STAT = 'OS' group by w.INVENTORY_GRP_DESC, we.INVENTORY_STAT

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, NVL(SUBSTR(ITEM.SKU,1,14),' ') as SKU FROM ITEM WHERE ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP='sli' GROUP BY NVL(SUBSTR(ITEM.SKU,1,14),' ')
